   <talk_paragraph index="n212_argenta-3-a" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300020" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Argenta.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n212_argenta-3-b" mid="94" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Argenta$<BR>Humans never change. the Ancients and the current day humans are all same to me. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Argenta caresses the rune)</FONT> This rune also used to be in a complete form, but the humans foolishly broke it into pieces.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n212_argenta-3-b" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300020" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Argenta.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n212_argenta-3-c" mid="96" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="95"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>What happened?</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n212_argenta-3-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Argenta.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n212_argenta-3-d" mid="97" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>$Argenta$<BR>There must have been some Ancients who had evil plans. They carried out an <FONT color=#a82424>experiment</FONT> that <FONT color=#a82424>shouldn't have been done</FONT>. You know, some people just do things they are not supposed to and can't clean up the shitty mess that they've made. This wouldn't have happened if all humans were naive and stupid like you.<BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>(Argenta frowns)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n212_argenta-3-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Argenta.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n212_argenta-3-e" mid="98" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Argenta$<BR>Anyway, I'm going to create the <FONT color=#a82424>Ancient Priest's Rune</FONT> with these. It's just like bringing the puzzle pieces together. Even a child can do it, but you can't so I'm doing it for you. Take it as an honour.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n212_argenta-3-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Argenta.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n212_argenta-3-f" mid="100" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="99"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>Of course. Thank you.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n212_argenta-3-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Argenta.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n212_argenta-3-g" mid="101" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Argenta$<BR>I said it's easy but that doesn't mean it won't take long. This would take time even for someone like me.<BR>You should get some training in the meanwhile.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n212_argenta-3-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="NPC_Right_Argenta.dds" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n212_argenta-3-h" mid="103" select_type="2" />
      <talk_question mid="102"><![CDATA[<html>${user_nick}$<BR><FONT color=#662500>I'll go to the Royal Castle ad make a report then.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
